Bachelorette;;2012;;R;;Comedy,Romance;;5.3;;Leslye Headland;;Kirsten Dunst,Isla Fisher,Lizzy Caplan,James Marsden,Rebel Wilson,Paul Corning,Andrew Rannells,Anna Rose Hopkins,Sue Jean Kim,Horatio Sanz,Hayes MacArthur,Kyle Bornheimer,Ann Dowd,Adam Scott,Ella Rae Peck,Megan Neuringer,Leslie Meisel,Jenn Schatz;;On the night of one of their old high school friend's wedding three irresponsible and capricious bridesmaids reunite for one last bachelorette bacchanal in the Big Apple. They unintentionally create a mess of their best friend Becky's wedding dress, before she marries her sweetheart Dale. They attempt to repair the situation by spending the evening before and morning of the wedding desperate to get the dress to Becky on time before the wedding starts, whilst discovering themselves and what they truly want from their lives along the way.;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt1920849/